# =====================================================================
# ClaudeCode — 私有/敏感路径绝对禁止入仓
# 规则形态：先全锁，再 allowlist 个别公开占位
# =====================================================================

# --- 个人/隐私层（最高优先级）-----------------------------------------
# private/ 内默认全部 ignore，再 allowlist 极少数公开占位
# gitignore 深层 allowlist 必须先 un-ignore 父目录，再控制其内部
private/*
!private/README.md
!private/CLAUDE.example.md
!private/AGENTS.example.md
!private/.env.example
!private/notes/
!private/secrets/
# notes/ 与 secrets/ 内部默认 ignore，仅放行 .gitkeep
private/notes/*
private/secrets/*
!private/notes/.gitkeep
!private/secrets/.gitkeep

_private/
.private/
**/private.local.*
**/secrets.local.*

# --- AI 助手私人指令文件（任何位置，根级或子目录）---------------------
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
AGENTS.md
AGENT.md
GEMINI.md
.claude/
.codex/
.gemini/

# --- 长期记忆 / 笔记 --------------------------------------------------
# 这里的 notes / journal 锚到根，避免与 private/notes/ 的 allowlist 冲突
memory/
/notes/
todo.local.md
/journal/

# --- 调研产物 / 子代理输出（非源代码）---------------------------------
_codex-out/
_gemini-out/
_research/
_scratch/

# --- 第三方参考源（许可证混杂，仅本地使用）---------------------------
ReferenceSource/

# --- 凭据 / 环境 ------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.secret
*.secret.*
*.key
*.pem
*.pfx
credentials.json
service-account*.json

# --- 构建产物 / 依赖 --------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
dist/
build/
out/
.bun/
.cache/
.turbo/
.next/
.parcel-cache/
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- IDE / OS ---------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- 日志 / 临时 ------------------------------------------------------
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
